rly phase of cluster formation, as inferred from our\nresults, the densest parts in the protocluster have had an accelerated\nformation of massive galaxies. We expect that these eventually grow and\ntransform into early-type galaxies at the bright end of the red sequence as\nseen in present-day rich clusters of galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Aug 2017 18:01:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Sep 2017 07:05:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-02"}
