l section we describe\nsome aspects of the drawing algorithm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Aug 2017 22:51:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 31 Aug 2017 07:51:55 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 May 2018 11:41:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 17 Jan 2020 10:26:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-20"}
